7-11T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"一定degree 啦 你一畢業九萬幾人同你爭幼教你就揼春點解當年唔讀degree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8574f8298336d32e05192cd93bfb33ddd77f8e3","tid":738351,"uid":193271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59d3892df3cb17dd4da510671b0699894e3b885","tid":738351,"uid":182877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"有d幼稚園校長會覺得有degree會好d，因為隨住優質免費幼稚園普及化，所以好多校長都會鐘意degree老師，又會叫已做緊幼稚園既老師進修。<br />\n但依行流失率都幾大，所以hd，degree都會搵到工，而且教大幼教都歷史悠久，實習又多。一d都唔輸蝕比 bu degree。有 edu hd一出黎都搵到正教，有21000人工。hd仲可以比讀degree賺多兩年錢。之後仲可以報pt degree 半工半讀。<br />\n一邊做一邊pt讀會好辛苦，如果真係pt讀最好係幼稚園做左一年先習慣左上左手再報讀都唔遲。<br />\n所以兩個都差唔多，睇你想一次過讀曬先定想邊做草經驗邊讀。不過後者係辛苦好多。<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf6ca1c09fa4748c9a53935f85df41b36faf7f0","tid":738351,"uid":45479,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"BU CIE係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e138ffe8cbb3edf381481e4b41dc6b6c2607c06e","tid":738351,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"你今日讀DEGREE早啲畢業 <br />\n早一年搵錢個錢都係度啦"}]}